text: Haplocoelum trigonocarpum is a species of plant in the family Sapindaceae. It is found in Kenya, Mozambique, Somalia, and Tanzania. It is threatened by habitat loss. == See Also == * Sapindaceae * Plant * Eudicots ==Sources== * World Conservation Monitoring Centre 1998.
